title: TV5Monde Thalassa 2016 Arctique-Antarctique les givres des poles
description:
Arctique-Antarctique: les givres des poles

Travel Documentary hosted by Georges Pernoud, published by TV5Monde broadcasted as part of TV5Monde Thalassa series in 2016 - French narration. 
http://docuwiki.net/images/f/ff/Arctique-Antarctique-les-givres-des-poles-Cover.jpg

Information
------------------------------
Arctic-Antarctic: The Frosted Poles.

For centuries, the Arctic and Antarctic have attracted very different personalities. All suffered physically, often paying a high price, to reach these promised lands.
